stepTitle: If you had data showing everyone who likes pistachio ice cream also likes strawberry ice cream, what is a question you might expect, and be prepared to answer?
choices: Are there other attributes strawberry and pistachio lovers have in common?
Do all people who like strawberry like pistachio?
Are there other flavors pistachio lovers crave? That is, are they just more $$open-minded$$ than others?
